	 @item
	 Script setting the time on your IP enabled thermostats.  Recommend setting the time every month.  Clocks are always gaining or loosing a few seconds here and there, to the point that it adds up to a few minutes here and there.  Setting the time on a regular monthly basis avoids the whole gaining and loosing problem.
